title: PSA to all living in Australia: Stay away from NA for the next few years!
body:
I really wish I was living in Australia right now. Sure there are deadly animals that will try to kill you, but I much prefer those over the three possible candidates we have for president:

* An old witch who has committed criminal activities
* An old guy who is literally a socialist
* Another guy who has the largest ego in the world (might be tolerable)

Get me out of here pls
